{
  "id": "adv_event_2304_01_02",
  "title": "近すぎて\n話せない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がライブの最後によく歌ってた……\nああ、あの曲ですか。確かにいいかもしれないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm‚ that song Mana often sang at the end of her live…\nAh‚ that song‚ right? It might be a good choice indeed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.5228801727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "二人で勝手に話を進めないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't just talk amongst only two of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.709546725,
      "endTime": 13.0934016387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだそうだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that's right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2867349625,
      "endTime": 15.233333333300001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん。ちゃんと説明するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. I'll explain properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4990700404,
      "endTime": 18.4466663997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "昔ね、麻奈ちゃんがライブの最後によく歌ってた\n曲があるの。麻奈ちゃん、とっても気に入ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ there's a song that Mana-chan often\nsang at the end of her lives. Mana-chan really liked it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6399997235,
      "endTime": 26.8280040266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……この間サニピのみんなで観たライブ映像で\n歌ってた曲のこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… You mean the song we watched together with\nall the Sunny Peace members the other day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0213373026,
      "endTime": 33.9946704706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、最後の曲の時……\n遙子さん、しんみりしてた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ during the last song…\nHaruka-san‚ you seemed a bit sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1880036514,
      "endTime": 41.1413144272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、バレてたかー\nそうそう、その曲のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ you noticed‚ huh?\nYeah‚ that's right‚ about that song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3346476556,
      "endTime": 46.9244664193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈はその曲を「いつか後輩が出来たら\n星見プロのみんなで一緒に歌いたい」って言ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana wanted to sing that song together with all\nthe Hoshimi Pro. members someday‚ she said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1177996954,
      "endTime": 54.3844663939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "いつか後輩が出来たら、って……\n遙子ちゃんは一緒に歌わなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someday‚ huh…\nDidn't you sing with her‚ Haruka-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5977997464,
      "endTime": 60.4976650587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "何度か誘ってもらったことはあったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was invited a few times‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6057814917,
      "endTime": 63.7186386427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも……その時は本っっっ当に人気も実力も\nまだまだで、自信が全く持てなかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but at that time… I was still far from being popular or skilled.\nI had no confidence at all‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.905305195,
      "endTime": 71.8657132149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "だから、麻奈ちゃんに誘ってもらえるのは\nとっても嬉しかったんだけど、いつも断ってたのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so I always declined\neven though it was pleased to be offered by Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0790463766,
      "endTime": 79.80981725070001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "当時は苦労をかけてしまい申し訳ないです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for causing you trouble back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0231506031,
      "endTime": 83.3404974621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "もう、気にしなくていいってば\n{user}君は凄く頑張ってくれたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ don't worry about it.\nYou really did your best for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5338307382,
      "endTime": 89.0819257737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "でも……今なら、一緒に歌えるかな、私も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I wonder if I could sing together now‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.2952592215,
      "endTime": 94.82988503780001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruka-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2032157422,
      "endTime": 96.8555967332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……その曲、歌おうよ！\n私、すっごく歌いたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Let's sing that song!\nI really want to!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0489300331,
      "endTime": 102.54458059470001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんの曲を今の私達が歌う……\n祭典も盛り上がりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Us singing Mana-san's song… The festival will\nsurely be exciting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7954606296,
      "endTime": 110.37872574330001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "曲の理解を深めるために、映像を確認しましょうか\n出来れば複数点確認したいところですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we check the video to better understand the song?\nIdeally‚ I'd like to check several‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5653924387,
      "endTime": 118.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら……麻奈さんのライブ映像\nすずちゃんと手分けしてかき集める。むん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… I'll gather Mana-san's live footage\nwith Suzu-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0858875354,
      "endTime": 125.653733166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはどう思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think‚ Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8537330706,
      "endTime": 127.6740731556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "うん……いいと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I think it's a good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8674065271,
      "endTime": 130.0193793455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "何か相談事があれば、いつでも言ってくれ\n……よし、それじゃあ決まりだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have any concerns‚ feel free to tell me anytime.\n…Alright‚ then‚ it's decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2260460216,
      "endTime": 136.4550120669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――合同レッスン初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The first day of joint lesson",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.2550120669,
      "endTime": 138.4283477145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、はっ、は……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah‚ hah‚ hah…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4283517835,
      "endTime": 146.3056534765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。ちょっと休憩にしよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Shall we take a little break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1990143137,
      "endTime": 152.1329597788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、だいぶ長い時間練習してたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we've been practicing for quite a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3262931027,
      "endTime": 156.4766785302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃。動きのキレが悪いけど……大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono. Your moves seem a bit heavy… Are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6633450824,
      "endTime": 162.78767636600003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ごめん、別に体調が悪い訳じゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Sorry‚ I'm not feeling unwell or anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.9943429469,
      "endTime": 168.0575403689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
