      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 288.0388070342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、時間ある？\nちょっと、お姉さんとお茶でもしよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ do you have some time?\nHow about we grab some tea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.0388070342,
      "endTime": 294.61093847719997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 295.8609386679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "――そっか。琴乃ちゃんが悩みを\n話してくれなかったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――I see. Kotono didn't open up\nabout her worries.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.9109386679,
      "endTime": 302.1308028456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 302.324136074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "うん。……ねえ、遙子ちゃん\nサニピと月ストは……ずっと一緒に頑張ってきたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Hey‚ Haruka-chan.\nSunny Peace and Moon Tempest… They've been working hard together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.324136074,
      "endTime": 311.9577740745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 312.1983634389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そうね。楽しい時も、苦しい時も\n肩を並べて進み続けてきたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… We've been walking side by side through both\nthe good times and the tough times.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.1983634389,
      "endTime": 320.5717420017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 320.7584086493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、今は琴乃ちゃんと距離が出来てる気がする\n今までみたいに気軽に話せないっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… But it feels like there's distance between Kotono-chan and us now.\nIt's not as easy to talk like before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.7584086493,
      "endTime": 330.7005852775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に、トップアイドルを目指そうって\n言ってたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we used to say we'd aim to be top\nidols together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.8872518297,
      "endTime": 336.1626260515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
