      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 336.3559592799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、さくらちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Sakura-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.3559592799,
      "endTime": 338.0244407412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 338.3596371408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと近くにいるからこそ\nかえって言えないことってあるって思うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sometimes‚ precisely because we're close‚\nthere are things we can't say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 338.3596371408,
      "endTime": 343.69312922909995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 343.8864624098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "近くにいるからこそ……言えないこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because we're close… there are things you can't say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.8864624098,
      "endTime": 347.8763489798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 348.0896823323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ましてや私達は――\nそれぞれプライドを持ってアイドルをやってるからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially us――\nBecause we each have our own pride as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 348.0896823323,
      "endTime": 353.35986379739995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
